<li id="cite_note-goarch-repentance-14">^ <a href="#cite_ref-goarch-repentance_14-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-goarch-repentance_14-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> John Chryssavgis, <a href="http://www.goarch.org/en/ourfaith/articles/article8493.asp" class="external text" title="http://www.goarch.org/en/ourfaith/articles/article8493.asp" rel="nofollow">Repentance and Confession - Introduction</a>, <a href="/wiki/Greek_Orthodox_Archdiocese_of_America" title="Greek Orthodox Archdiocese of America">Greek Orthodox Archdiocese of America</a>, accessed <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2008-03-21"><a href="/wiki/2008" title="2008">2008</a>-<a href="/wiki/March_21" title="March 21">03-21</a></span>.</li>
